story-context.interfaces:
**ApiEndpoint Decorator Interface:**
```typescript
interface ApiEndpointOptions {
  type?: any;              // Response DTO class
  isPaginated?: boolean;   // Use paginated response class
  isPublic?: boolean;      // Skip auth decorators
}

function ApiEndpoint(summary: string, options?: ApiEndpointOptions): MethodDecorator
```

**CRUD Shortcut Decorators:**
```typescript
// All return MethodDecorator
ApiGetAll(type: any)      // Paginated list with summary "Tümünü listele"
ApiGetOne(type: any)      // Single item with summary "Detayı getir", includes 404
ApiCreate(type: any)      // Create with summary "Yeni kayıt oluştur", 201 response
ApiUpdate(type: any)      // Update with summary "Kaydı güncelle", includes 404
ApiDelete()               // Delete with summary "Kaydı sil", 204 response, includes 404
```

**Factory Functions (from Story 8.2):**
```typescript
// Located at: src/common/swagger/api-response.factory.ts
createApiResponseClass(DataDto: Type): Type<ApiResponse>
createPaginatedApiResponseClass(DataDto: Type): Type<PaginatedApiResponse>
class ErrorApiResponseClass { success: false, status: number, message: string, errors?: string[] }
```

**Response Interfaces:**
```typescript
interface ApiResponse {
  success: boolean;
  status: number;
  data: T;
  message: string;
}

interface PaginatedApiResponse {
  success: boolean;
  status: number;
  data: T[];
  count: number;
  message: string;
}
```

**Swagger Decorators to Use:**
```typescript
import {
  ApiTags,              // Controller grouping
  ApiOperation,         // Endpoint summary
  ApiBearerAuth,        // JWT auth requirement
  ApiOkResponse,        // 200 success response
  ApiCreatedResponse,   // 201 created response
  ApiNoContentResponse, // 204 no content response
  ApiBadRequestResponse,    // 400 error
  ApiUnauthorizedResponse,  // 401 error
  ApiNotFoundResponse,      // 404 error
  ApiParam,             // Path parameter
  ApiQuery,             // Query parameter
  ApiBody,              // Request body
  ApiConsumes,          // Content type (multipart/form-data for file upload)
  ApiProperty,          // DTO field documentation
  ApiPropertyOptional,  // Optional DTO field
} from '@nestjs/swagger';
```
